# Contact form delivery (app/api/contact) · Resend
# Create a free key at https://resend.com → API Keys, then set this in Vercel
# project settings (Production + Preview) and in .env.local for local dev.
# Without it, the contact form falls back to opening a mailto: draft.
RESEND_API_KEY=

# Google Analytics 4 · optional override for the Measurement ID (GA4 Admin → Data
# Streams, G-XXXXXXXXXX). The app already defaults to the site's ID and only loads
# GA in production, so this is only needed to point analytics at a different property.
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=
